{
  "info": {
    "name": "FinTrack API",
    "description": "Sistema de Organização Financeira Pessoal com IA\n\n**Como usar:**\n1. Faça login em `POST /auth/login`\n2. O token é salvo automaticamente na variável `{{accessToken}}`\n3. Todos os endpoints autenticados já usam `{{accessToken}}` automaticamente",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "accessToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "connectToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "pluggyItemId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "connectionId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "sessionId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "simulationId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "budgetId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "goalId", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Registrar usuário",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "register"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"joao@email.com\",\n  \"name\": \"João Silva\",\n  \"password\": \"Senha@1234\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "  console.log('✅ accessToken salvo automaticamente');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"joao@email.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Senha@1234\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Banking (Pluggy - Open Finance)",
      "description": "Fluxo completo:\n1. GET connect-token → copia connectToken\n2. Abre widget Pluggy com o token (use o script pluggy-widget.html)\n3. Autoriza Nubank ou Inter no widget\n4. Widget retorna itemId → copia\n5. POST /connections com o itemId\n6. Aguarda sync (alguns segundos)\n7. GET /connections para ver status\n8. GET /connections/:id/accounts para ver contas e saldos",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Obter Connect Token (para widget)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.connectToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('connectToken', json.connectToken);",
                  "  console.log('✅ connectToken salvo:', json.connectToken);",
                  "  console.log('👉 Agora abra o pluggy-widget.html no browser e use este token para conectar seu banco.');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/connections/connect-token", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["connections", "connect-token"] }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Registrar conexão (após widget retornar itemId)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.connectionId) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('connectionId', json.connectionId);",
                  "  console.log('✅ connectionId salvo:', json.connectionId);",
                  "  console.log('🔄 Sincronização iniciada em background. Aguarde ~10s e execute GET /connections.');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/connections", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["connections"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"itemId\": \"{{pluggyItemId}}\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Listar conexões (verificar status sync)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/connections", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["connections"] }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "4. Ver contas e saldos da conexão",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/connections/{{connectionId}}/accounts", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["connections", "{{connectionId}}", "accounts"] }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "5. Disparar re-sync manual (simula webhook Pluggy)",
          "description": "Simula o webhook que o Pluggy envia quando o item é atualizado. Em produção, o Pluggy chama este endpoint automaticamente. Use para forçar re-sincronização de transações.",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/connections/webhook", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["connections", "webhook"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"event\": \"item/updated\",\n  \"itemId\": \"{{pluggyItemId}}\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "6. Remover conexão bancária",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/connections/{{connectionId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["connections", "{{connectionId}}"] }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Financial (Transações)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar transações",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/transactions?page=1&limit=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["transactions"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "from", "value": "2026-06-01", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "to", "value": "2026-06-30", "disabled": true }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Relatório de gastos por categoria",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/transactions/report",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["transactions", "report"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "from", "value": "2026-06-01", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "to", "value": "2026-06-30", "disabled": true }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Budgeting (Orçamentos)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Criar orçamento",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('budgetId', json.id);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/budgets", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["budgets"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"categoryId\": \"uuid-da-categoria\",\n  \"limitAmount\": 500.00,\n  \"period\": \"MONTHLY\",\n  \"startDate\": \"2026-06-01\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar orçamentos",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/budgets", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["budgets"] }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Excluir orçamento",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/budgets/{{budgetId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["budgets", "{{budgetId}}"] }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "5. Goals (Metas)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Criar meta financeira",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('goalId', json.id);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/goals", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["goals"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Reserva de Emergência\",\n  \"type\": \"EMERGENCY_FUND\",\n  \"targetAmount\": 30000.00,\n  \"deadline\": \"2027-12-31\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar metas com progresso",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/goals", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["goals"] }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "6. Financing (Financiamentos)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Criar simulação SAC",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('simulationId', json.id);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/financing/simulations", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["financing", "simulations"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Apartamento Centro - SAC\",\n  \"propertyValue\": 500000.00,\n  \"downPayment\": 100000.00,\n  \"loanMonths\": 360,\n  \"monthlyRate\": 0.8,\n  \"amortizationType\": \"SAC\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
